data.description: Welcome Home! Indulge in contemporary luxury with this beautiful 2-bed, 1-bath upstairs condo.  This open floorplan boasts vaulted ceilings, seamlessly connecting the living area and cozy kitchen and dining area and breakfast bar.  Enjoy the woodburning fireplace in the family room.  Window coverings throughout. The quiet and cozy gated community offers a pool, spa, tennis court, just went under fresh exterior painting done by the HOA. RV and Boat storage on property.  This is a MUST SEE!  HOA has rental restrictions so NO rentals. Your quiet piece of haven awaits!
